snippet.title: The Bunny Graveyard - Exclusive Chapter 1 Release Date Trailer | Black Summer 2023
snippet.description: The Bunny Graveyard: Chapter 1 will be available on Steam on September 22, 2023. Watch the trailer for The Bunny Graveyard to meet an adorable rabbit and get a peek at some nightmarish things that await you in this upcoming episodic horror adventure game. In The Bunny Graveyard, navigate through a dark, eerie, and sometimes cute landscape. Encounter bizarre creatures, make difficult choices, and uncover horrifying secrets as you join a bunny on an adventure to find the horrifying truth behind her existence.
